  <brief_title>Evaluation of LUM001 in the Reduction of Pruritus in Alagille Syndrome</brief_title>
  <acronym>ITCH</acronym>
  <official_title>The Evaluation of the Intestinal Bile Acid Transport (IBAT) Inhibitor LUM001 in the Reduction of Pruritus in Alagille Syndrome, a Cholestatic Liver Disease</official_title>
